                            <comment id="12362371" author="fuzzylogic" created="Wed, 11 Jan 2006 06:08:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Ant&apos;s general lack of list processing or loops would, in my opinion, make generating the list of locales to add to the manifest&apos;s classpath more trouble than it would be worth. I plan to resolve this issue by adding a static Class-Path entry to derby.jar&apos;s manifest.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
